cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

This paper focuses on quantization of weights and activations in deep neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision research (cs.LG, cs.CV). The paper also introduces several novel quantization algorithms, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper provides proofs and empirical analysis, which could be relevant to the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and robotics (cs.AR).
